                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Olivares</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d815fn1">Transmitted through the American Legation at
                        Tegucigalpa.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-08-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Olivares reports that Gens. Juan Estrada and Emiliano Chamorro arrived at
                    Nicaragua at 6 o’clock p.m. to-day.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
